---
import Button from "./Button.astro";
---

<div>
  <h2 class="font-bold tracking-tight text-current text-3xl mt-8 mb-4">
    Experience & Education
  </h2>
  <ol class="relative border-s border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-700 max-w-xl">
    <li class="mb-10 ms-4">
      <div
        class="absolute w-3 h-3 bg-amber-400 rounded-full mt-1.5 -start-1.5 border border-white dark:border-gray-900 dark:bg-amber-400"
      >
      </div>
      <time
        class="mb-1 text-sm font-normal leading-none text-gray-700 dark:text-slate-300"
        >March 2024 - Juny 2024</time
      >
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
        Web Developer React - JNC
      </h3>
      <p class="mb-4 text-base font-normal text-gray-800 dark:text-slate-200">
        Development of web applications focused on businesses, using React and
        MUI with good programming practices and clean architecture.
      </p>
    </li>
    <li class="mb-10 ms-4">
      <div
        class="absolute w-3 h-3 bg-gray-200 rounded-full mt-1.5 -start-1.5 border border-white dark:border-gray-900 dark:bg-gray-700"
      >
      </div>
      <time
        class="mb-1 text-sm font-normal leading-none text-gray-700 dark:text-slate-300"
        >September 2022 - March 2024</time
      >
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
        DAW course
      </h3>
      <p class="text-base font-normal text-gray-800 dark:text-slate-200">
        I'm very happy to have completed my DAW course. I have learned a lot of
        things, including Linux, MySQL, JavaScript, PHP, Laravel, React, Vue,
        Angular, and more.
      </p>
    </li>
    <li class="mb-10 ms-4">
      <div
        class="absolute w-3 h-3 bg-gray-200 rounded-full mt-1.5 -start-1.5 border border-white dark:border-gray-900 dark:bg-gray-700"
      >
      </div>
      <time
        class="mb-1 text-sm font-normal leading-none text-gray-700 dark:text-slate-300"
        >November 2023</time
      >
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
        CS50 Introduction to Computer Science - Harvard University
      </h3>
      <p class="mb-4 text-base font-normal text-gray-800 dark:text-slate-200">
        I have finished the CS50 course, where I learned a lot about computers
        and programming. I'm very happy to have completed this course. I gained
        knowledge in technologies like C, Python, SQL, HTML, CSS, and
        JavaScript.
      </p>
      <Button
        text="View Certificate"
        href="https://cs50.harvard.edu/certificates/3d787326-fdb2-42c6-acaa-ba67a0bb4e3a"
        target="_blank"
      >
        <svg
          class="w-3 h-3 ms-2 rtl:rotate-180 transition ease-in-out group-hover:scale-x-125"
          aria-hidden="true"
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          fill="none"
          viewBox="0 0 14 10"
        >
          <path
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            stroke-width="2"
            d="M1 5h12m0 0L9 1m4 4L9 9"></path>
        </svg>
      </Button>
    </li>
    <li class="mb-10 ms-4">
      <div
        class="absolute w-3 h-3 bg-gray-200 rounded-full mt-1.5 -start-1.5 border border-white dark:border-gray-900 dark:bg-gray-700"
      >
      </div>
      <time
        class="mb-1 text-sm font-normal leading-none text-gray-700 dark:text-slate-300"
        >September 2022</time
      >
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
        Full Stack Open - University of Helsinki
      </h3>
      <p class="mb-4 text-base font-normal text-gray-800 dark:text-slate-200">
        Driven by my desire to deepen my knowledge of web development, I
        embarked on this course. I am thrilled to have completed it and have
        gained valuable insights into technologies such as React, Node.js,
        MongoDB, GraphQL, TypeScript, and more.
      </p>
      <Button
        text="View Certificate"
        href="https://studies.cs.helsinki.fi/stats/api/certificate/fullstackopen/en/da07f9fc0b1776ed6ca619e7b88b60a0"
        target="_blank"
      >
        <svg
          class="w-3 h-3 ms-2 rtl:rotate-180 transition ease-in-out group-hover:scale-x-125"
          aria-hidden="true"
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          fill="none"
          viewBox="0 0 14 10"
        >
          <path
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            stroke-width="2"
            d="M1 5h12m0 0L9 1m4 4L9 9"></path>
        </svg>
      </Button>
    </li>
    <li class="ms-4">
      <div
        class="absolute w-3 h-3 bg-gray-200 rounded-full mt-1.5 -start-1.5 border border-white dark:border-gray-900 dark:bg-gray-700"
      >
      </div>
      <p
        class="mb-1 text-sm font-normal leading-none text-gray-700 dark:text-slate-300"
      >
        Some time ago
      </p>
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
        The Beginning of My Journey
      </h3>
      <p class="text-base font-normal text-gray-800 dark:text-slate-200">
        I embarked on my programming path by completing a foundational course on
        JavaScript, HTML, and CSS. Following the successful completion of the
        course, I transitioned into practical work and began my professional
        journey at a company, specializing in WordPress development. While
        working, I also took courses on freeCodeCamp to further enhance my
        skills.
      </p>
    </li>
  </ol>
</div>
